articles.title: One 'underdog' candidate sees opportunity in N.Y. maps mess - POLITICO
articles.description: Yuh-Line Niou is vying with better-known Bill de Blasio and Rep. Mondaire Jones, but she sees an opening with an electorate that is 20 percent Asian American voters.
articles.content: Niou knows she faces potentially better-funded and higher-profile candidates in the districts pileup of a Democratic primary. But if she can prevail, shed have a demonstrable impact on diversity in C… [+6513 chars]

articles.title: America's employers keep hiring despite high costs and a potential recession - CNN
articles.description: America's employers stand to have added hundreds of thousands of jobs in May even in the face of high inflation and recession fears.
